  "title": "BUSINESS DEVELOPMENT EXECUTIVE POSITION",
  "description": "<h2>🚗 <strong>WE’RE HIRING!</strong></h2><h3><strong>Business Development Executive</strong></h3><p>📍 <strong>Genesis Services Pte. Ltd.</strong><br />📍 Singapore</p><h3><strong>About Us</strong></h3><p>Genesis Services Pte. Ltd. is a growing automotive services company focused on vehicle rental, fleet services, and customer-centric solutions. As we expand our brand presence, we are looking for a <strong>dynamic, hands-on Business Development Executive</strong> to join our team.</p><h3><strong>Job Responsibilities</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Develop and execute <strong>marketing & branding initiatives</strong></p></li><li><p>Create and manage <strong>TikTok / short-form video content</strong> (cars, promotions, behind-the-scenes)</p></li><li><p>Assist in <strong>handling vehicles</strong>, including basic coordination and handover</p></li><li><p>Manage <strong>simple car photoshoots</strong> (listing photos, social media content)</p></li><li><p>Attend to <strong>walk-in customers</strong> professionally</p></li><li><p>Conduct <strong>vehicle handovers and returns</strong>, ensuring customer satisfaction</p></li><li><p>Support business development and daily operational needs</p></li></ul><h3><strong>Requirements</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Strong interest in <strong>automotive, marketing, and social media</strong></p></li><li><p>Comfortable appearing on or managing <strong>TikTok / video content</strong></p></li><li><p>Good communication and customer service skills</p></li><li><p>Organized, proactive, and willing to learn</p></li><li><p>Able to work independently and as part of a team</p></li><li><p>Possession of a <strong>valid Class 3 driving licence</strong></p></li><li><p>Prior experience in automotive / marketing is a plus (but not mandatory)</p></li></ul><h3><strong>What We Offer</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Competitive salary (based on experience)</p></li><li><p>Hands-on exposure to <strong>automotive & business operations</strong></p></li><li><p>Opportunity to grow with a fast-expanding company</p></li><li><p>Friendly and supportive work environment</p></li><li><p>Real involvement in branding and content creation</p></li></ul><p>📩 <strong>Interested applicants, please WhatsApp or send your resume to:</strong><br />📞 <strong>9818 8106 / 9146 0452</strong></p><p>📍 <strong>Location:</strong><br />351 Jurong East Street 31<br />#01-79 Singapore 600351</p><p></p>",
